Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.44,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}磨练自我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:16.81,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}唯我独尊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:18.92,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}既然诞生于此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.88,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那就请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.52,0:22:32.28,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天上天下唾手可得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.29,0:22:34.14,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}可来来去去尽是死路
